            <title>[LU-7478] Failover: replay-vbr test_10b: /mnt/lustre/f10b.replay-vbr-b: unexpected state</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7478</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Saurabh Tandan &amp;lt;saurabh.tandan@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/5a1e3efe-9131-11e5-ad50-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/5a1e3efe-9131-11e5-ad50-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_10b failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;/mnt/lustre/f10b.replay-vbr-b: unexpected state
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test log:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;CMD: shadow-40vm5 checkstat -v -p 0666 -u \#500 -g \#500 /mnt/lustre/f10b.replay-vbr-b
/mnt/lustre/f10b.replay-vbr-b has perms 0644, not 0666
replay-vbr test_10b: @@@@@@ FAIL: /mnt/lustre/f10b.replay-vbr-b: unexpected state 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
